## Why This Works When Other AI Initiatives Fail

Traditional AI consultants focus on tools. I focus on **re-engineering your systems** so the impossible choice disappears.

**Before:** "We have to choose between fast proposals or quality proposals."  
**After:** AI drafts 80% of proposals in your voice → your team only edits the critical 20% → 3x speed with higher win rates.

**This isn't theory.** I've eliminated trade-offs for SaaS companies, e-commerce brands, and professional services firms. The pattern is always the same: find where the trade-off lives, then redesign the handoff.

